        ]
      },
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/9/2/5/2",
      "text": [
        ": سألت أبا جعفرعليه السلام عن قول الله عزوجل يَحْكُمُ بِهِ ذَوَا عَدْلٍ مِّنكُمْ قال: العدل رسول الله صلى الله عليه وآله والامام من بعده ثم قال: هذا مما أخطأت به الكتاب"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.ammaar-muslim": [
          "2. [2/89] al-Kafi: Muhammad b. Yahya from Ahmad b. Muhammad from Ibn Fadhal from Ibn Bukayr from Zurara who said: I asked Aba Ja’far عليه السلام about the words of Allah Mighty and Majestic: “as ruled by two just men among you” <a href=\"/books/quran:5#h95\">[5:95]</a> – he said: the just man is the messenger of Allah صلى الله عليه وآله and the Imam after him, then he said: this is among that which the scribes made a mistake in."
        ]
      }
    },
    "verse_translations": [
